{
  "texts": [
    "These hybrid approaches involve combining various ML and DL methods to achieve better performance.",
    "Therefore, future research should prioritize the design and development of novel hybrid approaches in AHR.",
    "• Incorporating additional features: CNNs have proven effective in recognizing the spatial features of Arabic handwriting.",
    "However, incorporating additional features, such as temporal information, could enhance overall accuracy.",
    "For instance, the combination of RNNs with CNNs has demonstrated robustness."
  ]
}